    {
      "id": "602262",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "我送近平上西天",
        "uid": "13149"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t戴泳鏡 裝修3M防毒面具<br/>\n<br/>\n配置滅火隊，提個水桶 戴個燒銲手套 拿到就撿起來扔進去\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 3,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "602384",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "DEMfreedom",
        "uid": "103265"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t不是有晶哥讲了。n95口罩。护目镜，一个棍子。带刀每用刀只适合单打独到不适合群体。三件套。然后还可以带个帽子，这些都准备好了也不容易被监控识别。我记得还有衣服要穿黑色的，因为警察也是黑衣服可以混淆他们视野\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "602432",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "莫哈維郵差",
        "uid": "16611"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t可以參考一下之前香港的做法<br/>\n最重要的是泳鏡或任何不透風的護目鏡與工業用那種防毒面具, 隨身要帶水(飲用或沖眼用)<br/>\n<br/>\n如上面有人提到, 情況許可的話準備裝了水的水桶用夾子或燒銲手套撿起扔進去<br/>\n<br/>\n沒有的話先找東西蓋住減少氣體波及的範圍, 當年就有用那種吃飯用的不鏽鋼碟子與鑊蓋成功滅彈的美話 (<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWE0OGE0ZTdkMmU1OTRhODUwM2Q1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5a48a4e7d2e594a8503d5.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5a48a4e7d2e594a8503d5.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5a48a4e7d2e594a8503d5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGUwYzNjYTgxMTc3MTJlYWM2MGIzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/de0c3ca8117712eac60b3.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/de0c3ca8117712eac60b3.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/de0c3ca8117712eac60b3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
